files = glob('./data/assignments/*.csv', 
                   recursive = True)
df = pd.concat([pd.read_csv(f) for f in files], ignore_index=True)
df.loaded_distance = df.loaded_distance.apply(lambda x: x.replace(' mi', '').replace(',', '').replace('ft', '')).astype(float) # Formatting loaded_distance
df['origin'] = pd.Series(zip(df.origin_lat, df.origin_lng))
df['destination'] = pd.Series(zip(df.destination_lat, df.destination_lng))
df.appt_time = df.appt_time.str.replace(';', ':')
df = df.drop(['origin_lat', 'origin_lng', 'destination_lat', 'destination_lng'], axis=1)
df['trip_type'] = np.NaN
# df = df[:len(df)//100]
print(f"Shape of df: {df.shape}")

def cut_time(time):
    if len(time.split(':')) != 2:
        return 'other'
    if '00:00' <= time < '03:00':
        return '00:00 - 03:00'
    if '03:00' <= time < '06:00':
        return '03:00 - 06:00'
    if '06:00' <= time < '09:00':
        return '06:00 - 09:00'
    if '09:00' <= time < '12:00':
        return '09:00 - 12:00'
    if '12:00' <= time < '15:00':
        return '12:00 - 15:00'
    if '15:00' <= time < '18:00':
        return '15:00 - 18:00'
    if '18:00' <= time < '21:00':
        return '18:00 - 21:00'
    if '21:00' <= time < '24:00':
        return '21:00 - 00:00'
df['time_interval'] = df.appt_time.astype(str).apply(cut_time)

def AMPM_time(time):
    if time == 'AM':
        return 'AM'
    if time == 'PM':
        return 'PM'
    if len(time.split(':')) != 2:
        return np.NaN
    if '00:00' <= time < '12:00':
        return 'AM'
    if '12:00' <= time < '24:00':
        return 'PM'
df['AMPM'] = df.appt_time.astype(str).apply(AMPM_time)
